data.description: WOW! Beautiful updated 2-story home with a pool! This lovely updated 5-bedroom has a great floor plan! The gorgeous kitchen has sleek granite countertops, stone/glass tile backsplash, endless storage, & an island that opens to a large dining area. The formal dining & living have access to an enclosed patio w/view of the pool, firepit, covered patio, storage shed & lush lawn! Primary suite downstairs & 4beds/1 bath upstairs. Centrally located with water well and so much space!
